{"tid":852883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男陰莖離奇「長角」2公分…越切越長 醫生也傻眼","createTime":"2018-10-08T07:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T08:01:29.000Z","uid":205996,"like":142,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"44f804239d1be28ec6fbb2c539132d4847bf5c7a","tid":852883,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-12/656/20180912002928.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-09-12%2F656%2F20180912002928.jpg&d=R5Po8f5GjK4hF73s51Mjnp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=56494460\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-12/656/20180912002928.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n印度一名60歲男子日前發現，做完尿道手術後，陰莖竟離奇「長角」，靠切除手術也無法根治，不僅反覆生長，甚至還越來越長，宛如「人肉狼牙棒」，就連醫師也沒轍。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》報導，男子原本患有「硬化性苔癬」（lichen sclerosu），導致陰莖出現發癢、白斑等症狀，甚至影響尿道，在醫師建議之下，進行了尿道修復手術。沒想到術後2個月，卻發現自己的陰莖長角，嚇得他跑到喬治國王醫學（King George&rsquo;s Medical University）求助。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個角似乎有再生能力，就在醫師為他切除後，不久又再重新長回來，而且尺寸比前一次還長，一度達到2.5公分，之後又再度進行切除手術。<br />\n<br />\n男子的主治醫師阿嘉瓦(Ajay Aggarwa)對此也百思不得其解，推測是先前尿道手術後留下的後遺症；不過另一位醫學教授邦克（Chris Bunker）卻認為，男子陰莖長角與「硬化性苔癬」有絕對關係。"},{"pid":"8b8aa47189e4471a3c8f1af203b52206c5046bd7","tid":852883,"uid":44454,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"吞左粒腰果？"},{"pid":"1f5355d8a80e39e1871ffbd0bc61b94842f52524","tid":852883,"uid":9726,"like":272,"dislike":0,"score":272,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d83f6f2f52dfbe0ac8cb8f9b4d80cd8ab0feecc9","tid":852883,"uid":77355,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483cc58fd8eccb1e5d08a50d3a0e7876ccf7983f","tid":852883,"uid":34189,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"尖銳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking